254
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:57,140
Meskipun dia mencurigakan,

255
00:12:57,140 --> 00:12:59,240
dia adalah ahli forensik yang berbakat.

256
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:01,650
Benar.

